<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Caspar, uns hat <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan> Götfrid
                        Dieppolt, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie er etwas sache czehandeln hab mit
                                <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Hallemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, als ew das <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol
                                <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wirdet.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> darynne fürderlich sein wöllet. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
